  cinnamon-2.2.9.ebuild, cinnamon-2.2.13.ebuild:
  Cinnamon uses Adwaita from gnome-themes-standard as its default theme, and
  apparently crashes if the theme is not available (bug #512612, thanks to
  j.l.).

